						<p>Pāṇḍya, Māṟavarman Kulaśēkhara 1, •••= A.D. 1268-1312.</p>						

						<p>It seems to record that an individual of Maṭṭiyūr Śivapuri in Kēraḷasiṅga-vaḷanāḍu gifted some land as tax-free <hi rend="italic">dēvadāna.</hi> Perhaps he purchased the land from the ūrār of Kumārakuṟuchchi <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Kōdaṇḍarāma-nallūr.</p>						

